# Changelog

## - 2026-06-26
### Fixed
- Added exception handling in write_device() to resolve long-standing USB communication error (no retry/clear/reset on pipe stall)
- Added USB device release to open_device() in case of exception recovery
- Added to udev rule to disable autosuspend (just in case...)

## - 2021-02-18
### Fixed
- Restarting the driver now refinds the device on the USB bus. Fixes issue #1

## - 2021-01-04
### Added
- Copied udev rules over.

## - 2020-12-15
### Changed
- WMR200 driver split off of the mainstream WeeWX distribution, and made into a separate, unsupported, install.

